data.description: Awesome 4 bed/2 bath Ranch style home, with 2 year new roof & HVAC system, includes stove, dishwasher & refrigerator. Back yard has raised flower beds, deck for enjoying outside & dog run. Garage had been converted to studio type apartment which could be handy for in-laws or extra family but can easily be converted back to a garage. Overhead garage door still works. Conveniently located near grade school. Neighborhood great for those that like to take evening strolls or outdoor exercise. This won't last long as it's priced to sell!
